{
  "stem": "3453.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And graves were already prepared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took them in groups, each town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They took each town separately across the-- the hill, and Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When we walked in that day, Germans were sitting right on the hill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's the camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If-- this is the answer to the camp that the people were building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1942, after the ghetto was, of course-- after the ghetto was surrounded, and-- yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the ghetto was surrounded, the next day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next day, you know, we send out a man, one of our people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were about-- about-- what did I say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About how many people that were there in this-- in this hiding?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we sent out a man to find out what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he came back, a Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Loria ?], a very respected, nice gentleman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a-- he was a businessman before the war, and quite a well-to-do man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came running back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said they are [? appealing-- ?] they-- we must come-- come to the-- to the-- to the-- to the square.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If we are not, anybody who they'll find hiding, they will kill him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We-- we didn't, at that time, we didn't know that the verdict was the same for this one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I decided to-- to-- to-- to meet up with my family, with my-- with my family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I left them, and I went to-- with my family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was tough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, like I described you, in three-- there were three little rooms, 14 people, and the fear, [? everything ?] was horrible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At night, I remember we were not far from the gate of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at night the-- the people, the Christian people of not Jewish persuasion, had homes in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
